file.name: swagger.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
servers:
  - url: /v1
info:
  description: MRA Photo Resizer API
  version: "1.0.0-oas3"
  title: MRA Photo Resizer API
  contact:
    name: Aidan Carson
    email: aidan.carson@nginx.com
  license:
    name: Apache 2.0
    url: 'http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0.html'
paths:
  /v1/image:
    get:
      tags:
        - image
      summary: Test S3 link
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Return new image information
          content:
            '*/*':
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Images'
        '404':
          description: Image not found
      x-tags:
        - tag: image
      x-operationId: Images
    post:
      tags:
        - image
      summary: Resize Image
      parameters:
        - name: imageURL
          in: query
          description: The id of article to be fetched
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
      responses:
        '200':
          description: successful operation
          content:
            '*/*':
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Images'
        '404':
          description: Image not found
      x-tags:
        - tag: image
      x-operationId: NewImage
components:
  schemas:
    Images:
      type: object
      properties:
        thumb_url:
          type: string
        Large_width:
          type: string
        Medium_height:
          type: string
        Medium_width:
          type: string
        Thumb_width:
          type: string
        Thumb_height:
          type: string
        medium_url:
          type: string
        large_url:
          type: string
        Large_height:
          type: string
